This directory contains a minimal, pkgprobe-specific subset of the
PowerShell App Deployment Toolkit (PSADT) function library. The original
project is available at:

  https://github.com/PSAppDeployToolkit/PSAppDeployToolkit

These files provide the essential functions (Execute-Process,
Show-InstallationWelcome, Write-Log, etc.) needed to wrap GUI-only
Windows installers for Intune Win32 deployment.
